description: While solar panels offer environmental benefits,

rawPost.caption: While solar panels offer environmental benefits,
rawPost.description:
While solar panels offer environmental benefits, they can introduce significant health risks.

The conversion of direct current (DC) to alternating current (AC) by inverters generates ‘dirty electricity,’ which spreads through household wiring, leading to headaches, fatigue, and neurological disturbances .

Inverters create high magnetic fields and RF radiation from wireless monitoring systems, compounding electromagnetic exposure.

To ensure a safe environment, consult a building biologist before installing solar panels to mitigate these hazards.
